Fetches PKNCA Metadata

Source: R/NCA_Server.R
NCA_fetch_PKNCA_meta.Rd

Compiles Metadata from PKNCA

Usage

NCA_fetch_PKNCA_meta()

Value

Dataframe containing PKCNA metadata for NCA parameters.

Examples

PKNCA_meta = NCA_fetch_PKNCA_meta()
